<summary>Browse isotope and nuclear data</summary>
<developer id="io.github.e_j_w">
  <name translate="no">Jonathan Williams</name>
</developer>
<description>
  <p>A fast, offline viewer of isotope and nuclear structure data. Data is shown in the Chart of Nuclides or Segr√® chart format, which categorizes nuclides/isotopes based on their proton and neutron numbers.</p>
  <p>Features:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Display the chart with various color schemes: half-life/lifetime, primary decay mode, and more</li>
    <li>Select individual nuclides to browse data on ground and excited states, decay modes, gamma-ray energies, and more</li>
    <li>Runs locally, with no network connection needed</li>
  </ul>
</description>
